name: La Fiamma
infos: One of the most famous pitches in Switzerland and the must-climb of the Albigna area. A really exposed but well-bolted line climbs the south face of the 'flame'. One of the best summit shots imaginable! Two tricky moves. Watch for the hidden step at the fourth bolt!-Climb a route on the east face of the Spazzacaldeira or go there by foot. The obvious line on the summit spire!-7 bolts. Top anchor.
